{
  "title": "Piquant Brazilian Gouda Skewers",
  "description": "A tangy and chewy Brazilian dish featuring Gouda cheese, perfect for festive occasions, kosher-friendly and made with katsuramuki-cut cheese for a unique texture.",
  "cuisine": "Brazilian",
